---
// About section with modern design
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-24 bg-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-display heading-lg text-midnight mb-4">
        Why Artists Choose 
        <span class="text-gradient">ACE</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Because your creative business deserves a CPA who truly understands artists
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Content grid -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- Left column - Story -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-teal font-medium">
          <div class="w-12 h-px bg-teal"></div>
          <span>My Story</span>
        </div>
        
        <h3 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-midnight">
          From Artist to Artist Advocate
        </h3>
        
        <div class="space-y-4 text-slate">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            I started as a painter in Connecticut, juggling commissions, gallery shows, 
            and teaching gigs. Like you, I struggled with the business side — until I 
            realized that understanding my finances was the key to artistic freedom.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            After becoming a CPA and transforming my own creative practice, 
            I discovered my true calling: helping fellow artists build sustainable careers 
            without sacrificing their creative vision.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            Today, as a licensed CPA, I specialize in the unique financial needs of artists — from tracking 
            project-based income to maximizing creative deductions. Because I've been 
            where you are, I know exactly what you need.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 pt-4">
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl text-teal">10+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate">Years Experience</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl text-coral">50+</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate">Artists Served</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <p class="font-serif text-4xl text-amber">100%</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate">Artist-Focused</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right column - What makes us different -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="card-bold space-y-6">
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-midnight">
            What Makes ACE Different
          </h3>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-midnight">Artist-Specific Expertise</h4>
                <p class="text-slate mt-1">
                  I understand grants, commissions, residencies, and the feast-or-famine cycle.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-coral/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-coral" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-midnight">Creative Deduction Mastery</h4>
                <p class="text-slate mt-1">
                  I find tax savings in places generic accountants miss — from studio supplies to research trips.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-amber/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-midnight">No Judgment, Just Solutions</h4>
                <p class="text-slate mt-1">
                  Behind on taxes? Shoebox accounting? I've seen it all and I'm here to help, not judge.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal/5 to-coral/5 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-midnight mb-4">
            Ready to transform your creative chaos into financial clarity?
          </p>
          <button class="btn-primary">
            Schedule Your Free Consultation
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>